Class FNIRGImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FNIRG, Triplet, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class FNIRGImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements FNIRG
    An implementation of the model object 'FNIRG'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • GCGID
    • Char Inc
    • Ascend Ht
    • Descend Dp
    • Reserved
    • FNM Cnt
    • ASpace
    • BSpace
    • CSpace
    • Reserved2
    • Base Oset
